*Obavio* je svoje dužnosti za vreme trajanja zadatka. (He fulfilled his duties during the duration of the task.)

*Obaviti* ću obuku u ponedeljak. (I will complete the training on Monday.)

On je *obavio* sva potrebna ispitivanja. (He underwent all the necessary tests.)

*Obaviće* se čitav postupak. (The whole procedure will be completed.)

*Obavićemo* sva potrebna istraživanja. (We will carry out all the necessary research.)

On je *obavio* svoj posao vrlo brzo. (He finished his job very quickly.)